{"tid":1360992,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[投訴撚出動] 睇緊 ch85 傑志對曼城嘅全部同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-24T13:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T13:52:55.000Z","uid":83543,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84099403ac299acdb9d28e97a03f038741a975f8","tid":1360992,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"係咪覺得鍾仔好撚仆街?<br />\n係咪覺得班旁述 9up 好撚煩?<br />\n係咪覺得唔符合合理期望??<br />\n係嘅話, 就屌 CCTVB 老母!<br />\n<br />\n攻撃方向:<br />\n《電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 節目標準》<br />\n第9章 第3條 有關持平的一般準則<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvprog_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcommon%2Fpolicies_regulations%2Fcop%2Fcode_tvprog_c.pdf&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9acrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=a09e6f54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvprog_c.pdf</a><br />\n由於呢個喺比賽節目, 而且唱歌係可以影響到各方球員嘅, 所以絕對可以攞嚟做武器<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投訴表格在此:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9acrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=34486a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n節目名:<br />\n賽馬會傑志中心盃: 傑志 對 曼城<br />\n<br />\n播映時間: 20:21<br />\n<br />\n<ins>揀頻道嗰到, 揀完 ch85 要撳新增</ins><br />\n<br />\n投訴事項:<br />\n此比賽節目刻意迴避於香港大球場於 20:21 所發生的事件. 在20:21, 比賽踏入21分鐘時, 此比賽節目的現場聲音明顯被降低. 無綫電視的行為使觀眾不能準確地了解於香港大球場, 違犯《電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 節目標準》第9章 第3條 有關持平的一般準則中, 不應隱瞞事實並誤導觀眾的行為.<br />\n<br />\n(想投訴鍾仔嘅, 自己再寫)<br />\n<br />\n當 TVB 犯錯事, 相關嘅新聞節目如 新聞、時事節目、財經節目、個人意見節目、紀錄片、採用調查手法報道的節目、兒童教育節目、以醫療及健康為題材的節目、比賽節目 都可以用呢條入佢. <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油<br />\n沒有暴動只有暴政</span></span>"},{"pid":"d93aa35e37c3396a3bb20f2fb4e4436f09030cba","tid":1360992,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6417b17cb1a462d863a4fee6653161a780f11193","tid":1360992,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"點會係負皮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c5b45d0637a02ae35b4a450502bf7cebe256b8","tid":1360992,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93a5cfd9b9962eb480e99b8d063c491c3cd6c0a","tid":1360992,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:21:35.000Z","msg":"一齊推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a0559322635a56098111df5d7b63eccdf3081b","tid":1360992,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"你段嘢打好啲得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啲標點符號"},{"pid":"3a0bc3f558aafa10331dbd00e86c82c7a8a991dc","tid":1360992,"uid":14374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6417b17cb1a462d863a4fee6653161a780f11193","tid":1360992,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"點會係負皮啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i